The KSG weighs 6.9 lbs. and is as compact as legally possible with a 26.1” overall length and an 18.5” cylinder bore barrel. The grip and stock assembly is made of glass reinforced nylon (Zytel) and is easily disassembled by pushing out 2 pins, which store in 2 holes in the grip when removed. The barrel and pump assembly is removed by loosening the 2 front magazine tube nuts with a coin and sliding the assembly forward.

title: For Sale:  XDM 3.8 G-Code / Travis Haley "Blood-stripe" INCOG
postcontent: I have for sale a holster for an XDM 3.8 G-Code / Travis Haley "Blood-stripe" INCOGIt is in excellent condition and is the less common MARSOC tribute edition colors. This is the most comfortable holster I've ever tried. And is quickly put on or removed in seconds yet always secure. The draw from it feels smooth as glass.It will also fit an XDM 4.5 with a bit of muzzle sticking out beneath. Works great for appendix, or strong side carry. And equally well with 1 or both clips attached. Don't wait 8 weeks on back order. Get this and avoid sales tax as well. Willing to make arrangements to ship CONUS.See description below:The G Code / Haley Strategic INCOG inside the waistband (IWB) concealment holster is a joint development project between Travis Haley of Haley Strategic Partners and G Code Holsters. The G Code INCOG is a minimum bulk, multi-positional, deep concealment, high quality Kydex holster. Its distinctive features enable the concealed carry of a handgun from a variety of carry positions while facilitating the acquisition of a full firing grip on the weapon prior to the draw from the concealed carry. Inherent to the G Code INCOG are adjustments in the depth of concealed carry, angle of carry, the position of carry and security of carry. Adjustments are supported via the unique modular mounting points on the INCOG holster and the use of variable mounting components. Combined they maximize function respective to the users body type, concealed carry deployment tactics and personal preferences. The G Code INCOG holster is adaptive to varying operational environments and mission requirements. The mounting clip incorporates a negative angle designed to force the holster closer to the body. This improves the concealability of the holster without increasing the bulk and supports a higher positional carry without compromise to the positional security of the holster during use. This higher position facilitates faster weapon presentations from deep cover. The mounting clips also have multiple mounting points further increasing the range of carry options and adjustments. The mounting clips open and slide down over the belt and lock in place. The clip is actuated via a finger tab, and is flexed to open allowing quick installation or removal from the belt. All INCOG holsters come with Black FUZZ coating except for the Kryptek Typhon color option. Kryptek is a laminated fabric covering. At this time, PatriotTAC is ONLY selling the INCOG's with black FUZZ coating on our website. If you'd like to special order another coating/color, or ANY G-Code product, please contact us by phone, text, or e-mail.

This improves the concealability of the holster without increasing the bulk and supports a higher positional carry without compromise to the positional security of the holster during use. This higher position facilitates faster weapon presentations from deep cover. The mounting clips also have multiple mounting points further increasing the range of carry options and adjustments. The mounting clips open and slide down over the belt and lock in place. The clip is actuated via a finger tab, and is flexed to open allowing quick installation or removal from the belt. All INCOG holsters come with Black FUZZ coating except for the Kryptek Typhon color option. Kryptek is a laminated fabric covering. At this time, PatriotTAC is ONLY selling the INCOG's with black FUZZ coating on our website. If you'd like to special order another coating/color, or ANY G-Code product, please contact us by phone, text, or e-mail.
